Text: FW MDEA revised draft Cc therein Please call me if you would like to discuss Billy Original Message From Mann Kay Sent Wednesday April PM To Fleenor William Cc Manis Herman Subject MDEA revised draft Your esteemed colleague suggested I send this to you for your review Kay Forwarded by Kay MannCorpEnron on PM Kay Mann PM To Reagan nronXGate David nronXGate Ozzie nronXGate Lloyd CT Christi L CT Tom nron Edith CT Jim CT Edward nronXGate cc Subject MDEA revised draft Heres the latest notyetfinalbutgettingbetter agreement I may not have sent this to everyone who needs it but I know Reagan will take care of it Speaking of Reagan he is generating exhibits Kay

RE Water Supply Agreement Cc comments therein Original Message From Sole Carlos Sent Wednesday May PM To Manis Herman Fleenor William Subject Water Supply Agreement Please review and comment on the attached In particular you will note that the Notice to Proceed concept is addressed in Article V Thanks and as Kay repeatedly indicated in her voicemail I am out on vacation until Monday File Water Supply Agreement for Hart CountyDOC Carlos Sole Senior Counsel Enron North America Corp Smith Street Houston Texas phone fax

RE Deerfield development agreementcant open the open the attachment It must be protected or something You will probably have to save and reattach the file Original Message From Mann Kay Sent Friday June PM To Fleenor William Subject Deerfield development agreement Hi Billy Can you take a look at this since the Hermanator is out Thanks Kay Forwarded by Kay MannCorpEnron on PM Kay Mann PM To Lisa nronXGate Herman nronXGate Roseann nronXGate cc Ben nronXGate Steven nronXGate Subject Deerfield development agreement Hello The commercial team has asked that I forward this document to you for review It is a development agreement for a project in Florida We have attempted to address the accountingENext issues but please advise of any desired changes Thank you Kay File Deerfield development ag May DOC PS Pardon the formatting It will be cleaned up by those with the ability to do so
